Auto Remediation (pure DevOps)

This is most impressive to say in DevOps interview:

CloudWatch detects EC2 CPU > 90%
        ↓
CloudWatch alarm → Lambda
        ↓
Lambda automatically:
  increases ASG desired capacity
  adds more EC2 instances
  sends Slack alert "Auto scaled!"
        ↓
No human intervention needed ✅

Real companies: Netflix, Amazon DevOps teams

---

Security Automation (DevOps + Security)

AWS GuardDuty detects suspicious activity
        ↓
EventBridge → Lambda
        ↓
Lambda automatically:
  blocks IP in Security Group
  revokes compromised IAM credentials
  takes snapshot of affected EC2
  notifies security team
        ↓
Threat contained in seconds ✅

Real companies: Any enterprise security team

---
Log Processing (most relatable for DevOps)

Any production system:

Application writes logs to CloudWatch
        ↓
CloudWatch → Lambda (on error pattern)
        ↓
Lambda detects ERROR or CRITICAL
        ↓
Lambda sends alert to:
  Slack channel
  PagerDuty
  Email to on-call engineer
        ↓
Engineer gets notified instantly

Real companies: Every DevOps team ✅









